{"tid":820152,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中伏？Apple Watch 4 心電圖功能 港版未有定案","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T07:40:52.000Z","uid":118286,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"18c42fea4d23d07fbd85c5076c5f7605ed5ac043","tid":820152,"uid":118286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"原：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/15/apple-watch-series-4-ecg-only-available-to-us-market/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2Fapple-watch-series-4-ecg-only-available-to-us-market%2Flife-tech%2Fwatch-wireless-home%2F&d=4dVSf9W3uvtFrr7Xg0rPSzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=dd4a05d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/15/apple-watch-series-4-ecg-only-available-to-us-market/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前發表的 Apple Watch Series 4 有不少賣點，例如面積大超過 30% 的屏幕，有震動回饋的數碼錶冠等。其中最大賣點相信是是能夠隨時隨地進行 ECG 心電圖，不過該功能暫時只在美國市場提供，並且要等到今年稍後時間才正式推出，就算在 9 月 21 日上市，心電圖功能還是暫時缺席。<br />\n<br />\n網站 MacRumors 指出，雖然 Apple Watch Series 4 的硬件具備電極式心率感應器，但心電圖功能在美國以外的 Apple 官網都沒有列出，心電圖功能亦只在美國的新聞稿中有提及到。有分析指 Apple 公開表示 Apple Watch Series 4 的心電圖功能取得了美國食品藥品監督管理局（FDA）認證，受到對方監管。要在其他市場提供心電圖功能，估計亦要經過類似的審批認證過程。至於心電圖功能何時在美國推出，Apple 未有提供時間表，更遑論其他市場了。"},{"pid":"86eebb440810bcbb82281de000bb5e33f6048a7e","tid":820152,"uid":118286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:15:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3047b48e3f55f06c6097c83bee7fb6b47d465459","tid":820152,"uid":78399,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"無ECG根本無賣點， 真係你買埋我個份"},{"pid":"a7e7e24cfcd7b7ed26ae7b41d9aaa1fffaeaeafc","tid":820152,"uid":7178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"買英版如果港版無呢個功能"},{"pid":"4904c1940b6b604ca15639c5f0414bbc3e9ec362","tid":820152,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7e7e24cfcd7b7ed26ae7b41